comments: LaVine (CHI) places his off-arm against Murray (DEN), who is moving laterally into his path and marginal contact occurs.  LaVine then releases from the contact as he steps back.
Morris (DEN) makes marginal contact to Young's (CHI) arm and does not affect his control of the ball.
Young (CHI) cleanly deflects the loose ball from Porter Jr. (DEN) with his forearm during the rebound.
Young (CHI) intentionally lifts his leg and kicks the ball.
Young (CHI) maintains a legal guarding position defending Jokic (DEN) in the post.  LaVine (CHI) jumps to contest and avoids making contact with Jokic.
LaVine (CHI) gathers the ball as a progressing player and legally takes one step before releasing his dribble.
Jokic (DEN) makes marginal contact with Temple (CHI) during the pick.
Jokic (DEN) jumps vertically and maintains a legal vertical position as he absorbs the contact with LaVine's (CHI) body during his driving shot attempt.
Jokic (DEN) makes incidental contact with Young (CHI) as he gathers the ball in the backcourt.
LaVine (CHI) commits a take foul on Barton (DEN).
Temple (CHI) commits a take foul on Murray (DEN).
